BT 0 g /F2 14 Tf 188.4 740 Td (TIPS FOR SUCCESSFUL SUBSTITUTE DAYS) Tj ET
q 0.5 G 1 w 72 730 m 540 730 l S Q
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 700 Td (- Arrive 15-20 minutes early to review plans) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 678 Td (- Introduce yourself and write your name on the board) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 656 Td (- Review emergency procedures FIRST) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 634 Td (- Check for medical alerts before students arrive) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 612 Td (- Follow the teacher's routines as closely as possible) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 590 Td (- Be firm but fair - students test subs) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 568 Td (- Use the reliable student helpers) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 546 Td (- Don't take behavior personally) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 524 Td (- Leave detailed notes for the teacher) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 502 Td (- Keep your phone number for the teacher to follow up) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 480 Td (- If plans run short: read-aloud, silent reading, or journal writing) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 458 Td (- If technology fails: have a backup paper activity ready) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 11 Tf 90 436 Td (- Stay positive - your attitude sets the tone!) Tj ET

